rcirc-notify is a set of EmacsLISP functions for managing operating
system notifications from rcirc.

A customization group, {{{rcirc-notify}}} is provided which has a
range of settings.

It's best to install rcirc-notify via [http://marmalade-repo.org/packages/rcirc-notify/0.5|marmalade].

Alternately, copy the file to your load path and:

{{{
(require 'rcirc-notify)
}}}
